---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Polaroid from '../components/Polaroid.astro';
import amyPortrait from '../assets/photos/amy.jpg';
---

<Layout
  title="About Amy · Blackfen Little Learners"
  description="Meet Amy King, a qualified primary school teacher with extensive Early Years experience, opening a calm, home-based childminding setting in Blackfen, southeast London."
>
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="container-wide grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-12 items-start">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <Polaroid
          src={amyPortrait}
          alt="Amy King, founder of Blackfen Little Learners"
          aspect="aspect-[4/5]"
          rotate="rotate-1"
          caption="Amy"
          class="md:sticky md:top-28 max-w-sm mx-auto"
          priority
        />
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-3">
        <p class="eyebrow mb-3">About Amy</p>
        <h1 class="text-balance">Hello, I'm Amy.</h1>

        <div class="mt-6 space-y-5 text-ink-700/85">
          <p>
            I'm a qualified primary school teacher with extensive experience
            in the Early Years. After several years in the classroom I'm
            opening Blackfen Little Learners — a calm, home-based childcare
            setting where small children can feel genuinely safe, supported,
            and excited to learn.
          </p>
          <p>
            My approach is rooted in the Early Years Foundation Stage but
            shaped by years of watching what actually helps young children
            thrive: warm relationships, predictable routines, plenty of free
            play, and a grown-up who knows when to step in and when to step
            back.
          </p>
          <p>
            Practically, that looks like daily storytelling, songs, messy
            and sensory play, balanced meals, and lots of fresh air at our
            local parks and woodland.
          </p>
          <p>
            Outside of work I'm usually with family, baking, or pottering
            in the garden.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
          <span class="pill">Qualified primary teacher</span>
          <span class="pill pill-rose">Extensive Early Years experience</span>
          <span class="pill pill-sage">EYFS-led practice</span>
          <span class="pill pill-sun">Calm, home setting</span>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 card-tinted">
          <p class="eyebrow mb-2">A note for parents</p>
          <p>
            Choosing childcare is a huge decision. Once we're registered,
            I'd always recommend a visit so you can see the setting, ask
            questions, and see whether we're the right fit for your family —
            no obligation either way.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn-secondary mt-5 text-sm py-2 px-4">Register interest</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
